Jackie (Jackline) Nake Lumbasi bụ onye mgbasa ozi Kenya na-arụ ọrụ ugbu a na Kigali, Rwanda. O so mee The Big Breakfast Show na 91.3 Capital FM site n'afọ 2009 ruo 2018 ya na ọtụtụ ndị na-eme ihe ngosi gụnyere Gaetano Kagwa, Ramesh Gabalsing, Alan Kasujja, Marcus Kwikiriza na Oulanya yana ịgụ akụkọ mgbede na UBC na Uganda ruo afọ 2014.

Lumbasi hapụrụ ikuku Capital FM na Febụwarị 2018 wee sonye n'ọnọdụ ikuku n'otu ụlọ ọrụ ahụ mgbe mgbanwe zuru oke nke Big Breakfast show mana obere oge ka nke ahụ gasịrị ọ kwagara Royal FM nke dị na Rwanda iji mee ihe ngosi ụtụtụ n'asụsụ Bekee n'akụkụ Kwizera.
A maara ya nke ọma maka olu ya siri ike ma sie ike ma kpọtụrụ ya aha n'etiti ndị na-eweta redio a na-akwụ ụgwọ kachasị elu na Uganda.
Lumbasi malitere ọrụ mgbasa ozi ya dị ka onye ngosi na Power FM na Kampala
Mgbe ahụ ọ kwagara Capital Fm Uganda ebe ọ malitere ịnabata ihe ngosi nri ụtụtụ n'afọ 2009 mgbe ọpụpụ Lilian Mbabazi ruo 2018 mgbe a gbanwere ihe ngosi nri ehihie dum

Ọ kpughere ọpụpụ ya n'otu n'ime akwụkwọ vidiyo Flavia Tumusiime nke e kesara na Flavia na Capital FM's Facebook page. O nwetara onyinye ozugbo na Kigali Rwanda na Machị 2018 ebe ọ na-akwado ihe ngosi nri ụtụtụ na Kwizera

Jackie mere ihe ọchị banyere eziokwu ahụ bụ na ya na ndị aha ha na-amalite na mkpụrụedemede K arụkọwo ọrụ, na-ezo aka Alan Kasujja, Marcus Kwikiriza, Gaetano Kagwa na ugbu a na Rwanda, ebe ọ na-akwado ihe ngosi nri ụtụtụ a na-akpọ 'Kigali In The Morning', ya na Kwizera_Arnold.
